      ELSE.
        INSERT lv_profl INTO TABLE lr_delivery_group->gt_profl.
      ENDIF.
      CLEAR lv_threshold_dg_grp.
      CONTINUE.
    ELSE.
* For subsequent deliveries, keep capturing the DG profiles of the corresponding delivery
      READ TABLE lt_profl TRANSPORTING NO FIELDS
           WITH TABLE KEY table_line = lv_profl.
      IF sy-subrc NE 0.
