            IF lv_dg_grp IS INITIAL.
              EXIT.
            ENDIF.
          ENDLOOP.

* If a mismatch DG profile is found in the current package, exit the loop of the delivery
* DG profiles, and proceed to check for next package
          IF lv_dg_grp IS INITIAL.
            EXIT.
          ENDIF.
        ENDLOOP.

* If all the delivery DG profiles are a perfect match with all the existing DG profiles in
