* <SIGNATURE>---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* | Instance Private Method ZCL_MOT_CVC_REPORT_CNTRL->REFRESH_OVERVIEW
* +-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
* | [!CX!] ZCX_MOT_CVC_REPORT
* +--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</SIGNATURE>
METHOD refresh_overview.


  FIELD-SYMBOLS <ls_criteria> TYPE any.

  ASSIGN me->gr_last_selection->* TO <ls_criteria>.

  me->gt_data = me->go_model->get_data( is_selection_criteria = <ls_criteria> ).

  me->go_view->display_overview( iv_calc_type = me->g_calc_type ).

ENDMETHOD.


